      <section eId="sec_34_15_387">
        <num>34-15-387</num>
        <content>
          <p>The revision effective July 1, 2010, substituted "duty" for "obligation" in the first sentence of subsection (a); in subsection (b), in the first sentence, substituted "insurance coverage, and any other guarantee" for "insurance carrier, and from any other guarantor" near the middle, and substituted "reasonable administrative and legal costs" for "attorneys' fees and legal costs" at the end, and added the last sentence; and added subsection (c).</p>
          <p>The revision effective July 1, 2016, substituted "an insolvent participant" for "a bankrupt participant" in the second sentence of subsection (c).</p>
        </content>
